{"tid":1178593,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［英國撚］Sunday roast 其實好撚正","createTime":"2019-05-30T13:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T19:43:17.000Z","uid":221748,"like":32,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d8af16548d7857fec09894a368d771fbe51892dd","tid":1178593,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"介紹一下大家應該冇乜接觸過既隱藏英國菜Sunday roast<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSunday roast顧名思義就係星期日先有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多年前就係D人去完教堂食既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係歐洲都好常見 但英國人自己改變左少少 就變左人人都有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且好受英國人歡迎 差唔多每個星期日既pub同餐廳都逼滿晒人食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzWNkY0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzWNkY0.png&h=d00b73e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正常來講 Sunday roast 有四種肉揀 牛，豬，羊，雞 仲有素食版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iOfeLqT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOfeLqT.png&h=c48bb627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 油封鴨腿都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且唔同嘅餐廳都有少少唔同 例如牛嘅部位 我甚至食過乾式熟成既烤牛肉 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wAKCJdq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwAKCJdq.png&h=212c57b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n慢煮豬腩肉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMQFFZB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMQFFZB.png&h=a1fde045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和牛都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkGQ3dV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkGQ3dV.png&h=a2728ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁正常既Sunday roast入面除左肉之外 仲有烤薯仔 唔同嘅菜 仲有大家應該冇乜接觸過嘅約克郡布丁  再加上 牛肉汁 一份美味可口既Sunday roast就出世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家想睇多啲可以follow我 ig  我自費周圍食 就快破產 求包養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?igshid=oyk5hy4ski2c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffoodkiller_dk%3Figshid%3Doyk5hy4ski2c&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1SVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=20fab310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?igshid=oyk5hy4ski2c</a>"},{"pid":"894b192baf285f03784313360bd001f6533f55f3","tid":1178593,"uid":166890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"星期日試下先😂"},{"pid":"af84b1588c46fd2499c4b85d6119531926cbec2e","tid":1178593,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"894b192baf285f03784313360bd001f6533f55f3","tid":1178593,"uid":166890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"星期日試下先😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:53:30.000Z","msg":"係英國就要搵日試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 體驗下"},{"pid":"078db66ffe425abf49e2688ea397defc3d31c83c","tid":1178593,"uid":43964,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:11:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老屎根本gravy 90% 其他野10% 你試下無gravy,點撚樣食堆野。特別係油過閪既yorkshire pudding<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你識條鐵。根本稱唔上好撚好食"},{"pid":"e854c5570d7fb9848ab5351418f7b833b0783953","tid":1178593,"uid":221748,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"078db66ffe425abf49e2688ea397defc3d31c83c","tid":1178593,"uid":43964,"like":